import React from "react"; import "./Projects.css"; const Projects = () => (

Projects

Cerner Corporation:

  • 1.Worked on AI and ML-based life-saving leaf blower technology for Cerner.
  • 2. Wrote Call Home scripts using SQL, PL-SQL, T-SQL, VB Script, Power Shell, and database queries. Results stored in the Cloud Transport Service CCTS and displayed in Vertica & Lon databases.
  • 3. Improved Jetstream framework CSV reader and Call Home data collection framework.
  • 4. Created a Java Native Interface to fetch free disk space on Linux servers using JavaScript & C++.
  • 5. Enhanced server identification scripts and crash gather dumps data collection.
  • 6. Eliminated sensitive password display in the Millennium domain for the Olympus application using JavaScript.
  • 7. Streamlined Workflow Analyzer workflows using the new CorrelationID parameter and optimized timers.
  • 8. Designed a UI portal for CallHome utilizing the Django framework and Python.
  • 9. Wrote a JavaScript to create new datastores in the Olympus UI.

6D Technology:

  • 1. Constructed a React element for a tree structure using JSON and Reactstrap in the Magik UI project.
  • 2. Wrote services in SPRINGBOOT for the React tree view with CRUD operations.
  • 3. Implemented a feature in SMSC GUI to view MSISDN reports utilizing Java and JSP servlets

Probots Techno Solutions:

  • 1. Formulated a native C/C++ keycode API to interact with a REST API for controlling a kidney dialysis reprocessing unit for GK Healthcare.
  • 2. Developed an Android app with an API to connect with a GPS tracker kit for Alpine Star.
  • 3. Engineered a remote control that uses Bluetooth and enables recording and clicking of videos on RTMP and RTSP servers.
  • 4. Engineered a pet tracker app using Android, Arduino GPS, C/C++, REST API, Google Maps API, and JSON.
  • 5. Constructed a custom camera app that captures photos and QR codes with auto-focus.
  • 6. Implemented live video streaming with RTSP and RTMP servers.
); export default Projects;
